## Method B — Fenced block fallback (still supported)

If Method A is not available, embed a `json:chart` code block in any message.
The UI intercepts it in Markdown and renders the chart.

````
```json:chart
{
  "type": "line",
  "title": "Sprint Burndown",
  "xKey": "day",
  "yKeys": ["remaining", "ideal"],
  "data": [
    {"day": "Mon", "remaining": 24, "ideal": 20},
    {"day": "Fri", "remaining":  4, "ideal":  4}
  ]
}
```
````

