## Examples

### Sprint burndown

````
```json:chart
{
  "type": "line",
  "title": "Sprint Burndown",
  "xKey": "day",
  "yKeys": ["remaining", "ideal"],
  "xLabel": "Day",
  "yLabel": "Story Points",
  "data": [
    {"day": "Mon", "remaining": 24, "ideal": 20},
    {"day": "Tue", "remaining": 19, "ideal": 16},
    {"day": "Wed", "remaining": 15, "ideal": 12},
    {"day": "Thu", "remaining": 10, "ideal":  8},
    {"day": "Fri", "remaining":  4, "ideal":  4}
  ]
}
```
````

